plot: Jen is a bridesmaid in a friend's wedding, a stressful event compounded by uniquely She-Hulk issues.

Jen is invited to be a bridesmaid by an old high school friend that is getting married, and who makes Jen not to turn into She-Hulk on her wedding day and upstage her, Meanwhile, Mallory and Nikki help a man, Mr. Immortal, in a series of divorce settlements who "dies" to get out of boring marriages.—Gislef
